nodes.text: Zelosian wine was a type of beverage that was presumably alcoholic in nature.

It was served on the Red Moon Saloon at Mos Eisley, Tatooine. It was also involved in a major incident at the bar one night that resulted in Jabba's Force-sensitive Gamorrean guardsmen and Gamorrean brothers Thok and Gorc getting arrested by the Prophetess, involving seven barrels of the wine itself, Thok, Gorc, five fricasseed Ugnaughts, three bludgeoned-to-death Gungans, and a Kloo horn.
